  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the EUS registry is to record information about Endoscopic Ultrasound (EUS) on the
      management of gastrointestinal disease. The registry will evaluate efficacy, safety and
      technical success of the Endoscopic Ultrasound (EUS). Design is retrospective and prospective
      registry study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
